author: Tasha Hegarty
title: Gogglebox's Eve Woerdenweber announces her engagement and it's not to Silent Jay - Showbiz
text: #PrayForSilentJay: Gogglebox's Eve Woerdenweber has announced her engagement.Earlier this year, 'Silent' Jay announced the absolutely tragic news that Eve had broken up with him out of the blue.I was proposed to in Venice and I said yes to my lovely fiancé. I love you sweetheart @Josh1on1 pic.twitter.com/1Jo9cpJpYt— Eve Woerdenweber (@GoggleboxEve) September 23, 2015 Filming #gogglebox and trying not to stare at my beautiful ring from my beautiful fiancé & soul mate. #engaged pic.twitter.com/DIwCiqPnsw— Eve Woerdenweber (@GoggleboxEve) September 25, 2015 So according to some I look miserable these days...Yep...so miserable.... #getyourfactsright #happyaslarry pic.twitter.com/Gj3nZhDIQh— Eve Woerdenweber (@GoggleboxEve) September 30, 2015Jay said at the time: "Eve said she still wants to be friends but hasn't spoken to me and has deleted me on Facebook. It really hurts, we were so close."Despite the breakup, he was contracted to keep filming with the family for the rest of the series.Gogglebox airs every Friday at 9pm on Channel 4.
